## Configuration

{% set env_prefix = design.server_name | upper | replace('-', '_') %}
{% if design.backend and (design.tools | selectattr("impl.strategy", "equalto", "http_call") | list) %}
### Upstream service connection

This server proxies requests to an upstream HTTP service. Set this before starting:

```bash
export {{ env_prefix }}_BASE_URL=http://{{ design.backend.host }}:{{ design.backend.port }}
```

**The upstream service must already be running** before you start this MCP server.
