{% if design.enable_server_auth %}

### MCP server authentication

This server requires clients to authenticate via OAuth2 before connecting.

```bash
# Set the shared secret — users enter this in the browser login form
export {{ design.server_auth_env_var }}=<your-secret-token>
```

For remote deployments, also set the public URL so OAuth redirects work correctly:

```bash
export MCP_SERVER_URL=https://your-server.example.com
```
